{"tid":929899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【炸剩一隻手 靠指紋識別照樣入門口】 【內地創意智能鎖廣告遭共青團發文譴責後下架】","createTime":"2018-12-06T02:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T12:44:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"082da4a91ffbb3dc9e14a70fad34133f54ca2720","tid":929899,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"【炸剩一隻手 靠指紋識別照樣入門口】<br />\n【內地創意智能鎖廣告】<br />\n【遭共青團發文譴責後下架】<br />\n<br />\n最近內地一個廣告，引起不少人討論。影片中的拆彈專家，一次又一次奮勇接受任務。<br />\n<br />\n雖然勇氣可嘉，但技術就似乎不太好。每次拆彈，下場都是失敗。而每次失敗之後，拆彈專家回到家裡，父母都發現兒子樣子愈來愈不同。<br />\n<br />\n到底廣告是賣甚麼產品?原來它是一個智能鎖廣告，標榜就算拆彈專家炸剩一隻手，只要靠指紋識別，照樣能進家門。父母還可以透過手機應用程式，知道是誰開門，即刻放心了。<br />\n<br />\n不過不是人人都欣賞。除了網民，江蘇網警和共青團微博也發文譴責，罵它侮辱拆彈專家，把無知當創意。智能鎖生產商事後就發道歉信，指自己一直以來都保持對國家和民族的信仰，致力向公眾傳遞正確價值觀。知道廣告對大眾帶來不適，已經第一時間撤掉廣告，向公眾誠摯致歉。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#拆彈專家<br />\n#保持對國家的信仰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/?__tn__=kC-R&amp;eid=ARDFvMhGIvbSce_q_Xl4F2MxwpQbXYkhT1nbQ0xSY2uJoKMJ9Wde5BAGilzrDK18j4SqLKJR7_LOVjC6&amp;hc_ref=ART4laL8oSAFmztpCaKQiw3cnyQV-flykG1sgFQY5IU5E--74KNz5CqmSrfKwrLrvLI&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F%3F__tn__%3DkC-R%26eid%3DARDFvMhGIvbSce_q_Xl4F2MxwpQbXYkhT1nbQ0xSY2uJoKMJ9Wde5BAGilzrDK18j4SqLKJR7_LOVjC6%26hc_ref%3DART4laL8oSAFmztpCaKQiw3cnyQV-flykG1sgFQY5IU5E--74KNz5CqmSrfKwrLrvLI%26fref%3Dnf&d=FUNJkixV47%2Bc3WPZyQz53pUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=812025b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/?__tn__=kC-R&amp;eid=ARDFvMhGIvbSce_q_Xl4F2MxwpQbXYkhT1nbQ0xSY2uJoKMJ9Wde5BAGilzrDK18j4SqLKJR7_LOVjC6&amp;hc_ref=ART4laL8oSAFmztpCaKQiw3cnyQV-flykG1sgFQY5IU5E--74KNz5CqmSrfKwrLrvLI&amp;fref=nf</a><br />\n百變星君<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891e918e85a0c44a1122fe5f0d118a67889e31a7","tid":929899,"uid":192311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"智能鎖爆炸，